review: Annamalai sir is an extremely polite and knowledgeable doctor. He listens to your concerns. Examines and then gives you a clear picture of what the problem is and various options to solve it. I would recommend Annamalai sir 10/10 to anyone with any dental problems. **** **** ** **** * ****** *** ** ************** ****** *** ********

review: I had gone to Dr. Annamalai for my daughter's tooth alignment and was absolutely satisfied with the treatment.  He is so involved and dedicated and is passionate about his work and you will be amazed at the result.  This time I went for my teeth alignment and he was very patient in hearing me out fully.  He, after examining my x-ray advised me against the option and though disappointed that I had to live with my problem,  I  respect his advise as there is obviously no reason that he should advise me against it.  Doctors like Annamalai are very rare to find in these testing times and I am extremely happy to have found him. I wish him the very best in all his endeavors. God bless!

review:
Went to have self ligating braces for my kid. Doctor was friendly and soft spoken, explained different options in pre procedure appointment so we could choose right type of braces, very helpful with appointments. 

On the procedure day doctor started the procedure right on time as per appointment, was patient and detail oriented, made my kid feel comfortable throughout the procedure. Explained post procedure care in detail as well.
